  "texts": [
    "• Hosting services: A broad category encompassing online repositories that store and disseminate various types of third-party provided information at the request of users.",
    "Examples range from cloud infrastructure services, web hosting providers, app stores, online marketplaces, collaborative economy platforms, and social media networks.",
    "Hosting services are exempted from liability for user-generated illegal content if they have no knowledge of its illegal nature and act expeditiously to remove it once made aware.",
    "They are subject to DSA transparency requirements, notice-and-takedown obligations under Articles 14 and 15, and duties to provide information to authorities under Article 31.",
    "• Online platforms: A subset of hosting services that actively disseminate third-party information to the public."
  ],
